title: Arcadium - Breathe Awhile (1969) (with single) (mp3) (320 kbps)
description:
Arcadium - "Breathe Awhile" album (1969) (with bonus non-album 7" single) (mp3) (320 kbps)

Heavy UK psych/hard rock/prog/blues.

Originally released in November 1969 on the Middle Earth label, this reissue contains the two tracks from a 7" single issued that same month but not included on the original album.  Full artwork included here too.


Graham Best: bass, vocals
Allan Ellwood: organ, vocals
John Albert Parker: drums
Robert Ellwood: lead guitar, vocals
Miguel Sergides: 12-string guitar, vocals
